Unfortunately, your bet did not qualify for the bonus wagering requirements because it did not meet one or more promotion conditions.
The most common reasons are:
• A restricted market was selected (Handicap, Over/Under, Odd/Even);
• The odds were below the required minimum;
• The Cashout feature was used;
• The stake exceeded the €50 maximum limit;
• It was a repeated bet on the same event;
• The bet was placed on Virtual Sports.
If you provide your bet ID, we'll be happy to review it and explain exactly why it did not qualify.

