Order of Balance Usage When Placing Sports Bets
When you place a sports bet, your funds are used in the following order:
FreeBet / No Risk Bet (if available);
Real Money Balance;
Regular Bonus Balance.
This means that if you have an active FreeBet or No Risk Bet, it will always be used before your real balance.

